description.default: The main function is to realize S3/WEBDAV synchronization awareness when an unofficial subscription is made. At the same time, the synchronization function of an official subscription can also be optimized.
description.zh_CN: 主要功能为在非官方订阅的情况下进行S3/WEBDAV的同步感知，同时也可以对官方订阅的同步功能进行优化加速。
